```

### Typography
- **Headers:** Playfair Display (serif)
- **Body:** Lato (sans-serif)
- **Buttons:** Montserrat (sans-serif)

### Key Performance Targets
- **Lighthouse:** 90+ across all metrics
- **Page Load:** < 1 second
- **Core Web Vitals:** LCP < 1s, TBT < 100ms, CLS < 0.1

### Primary User Personas
1. **Beauty Enthusiast:** Female, 22-35, regular maintenance
2. **Busy Professional:** Female, 30-45, efficiency-focused
3. **First-Time Visitor:** Female, 18-25, trying services
4. **Returning Loyalist:** Female, 25-40, loyalty perks

### Core Features
- **Booking System:** Square POS integration
- **Membership Program:** Loyalty tiers and referral rewards
- **Gallery:** Before/after transformations
- **Blog:** Educational content for SEO
- **Reviews:** Google/Instagram integration

### SEO Keywords
- "lash extensions [city]"
- "brow services [city]"
- "beauty salon [city]"
- "lash fill [city]"

### Technical Stack
- **Frontend:** Next.js, React, TailwindCSS
- **Backend:** Node.js, Express
- **Database:** PostgreSQL, Prisma
- **Hosting:** Vercel (frontend), AWS/Heroku (backend)

### Critical UX Requirements
- Mobile-first responsive design
- One-click booking with clear CTAs
- Trust signals (testimonials, reviews, gallery)
- WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility compliance
- Fast loading with optimized images

### Business Goals
- Increase local search visibility
- Improve booking conversion rate
- Build brand recognition
- Implement automated marketing
- Create loyalty program for repeat clients
